// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1147 — Mass File Rename (onyx)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: cb87d079-af48-5718-bd18-11c6ab8fa9f2

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
